file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Minimal valid OpenAPI specification
  version: "0.1"
servers:
  - description: API server basepath
    url: "/v0"
paths:
  /health:
    get:
      operationId: get_health
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "health check in separate file"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HealthCheckEnveloped'
                #$ref: './components/schemas/health_check.yaml#/HealthCheckEnveloped'
  /dict:
    get:
      operationId: get_dict
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: "#/components/responses/EnvelopedDataResponse"
  /attobj:
    get:
      operationId: get_attobj
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: "#/components/responses/EnvelopedDataResponse"
  /envelope:
    get:
      operationId: get_envelope
      responses:
        default:
          $ref: "#/components/responses/EnvelopedDataResponse"
  /list:
    get:
      operationId: get_list
      responses:
        default:
          description: "fake desc"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/EnvelopedDataArray"
  /string:
    get:
      operationId: get_string
      responses:
        default:
          description: "default desc"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/EnvelopedString"
  /number:
    get:
      operationId: get_number
      responses:
        default:
          description: "default desc"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/EnvelopedNumber"

  /mixed:
    get:
      operationId: get_mixed
      responses:
        default:
          description: "default desc"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/EnvelopedArrayObjects"

components:
  schemas:
    EnvelopedArrayObjects:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            additionalProperties:
              type: string
        error:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
    EnvelopedNumber:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: number
        error:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
    EnvelopedString:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: string
        error:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
    EnvelopedData:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Data"
        error:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
    EnvelopedDataArray:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Data"
        error:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
    # -----
    Data:
      type: object
      properties:
        x:
          type: integer
        y:
          type: string
    Error:
      type: object
      nullable: true
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
        resource:
          type: string
        field:
          type: string
    # inline version of components/schemas/health_check.yaml ---------
    HealthCheckEnveloped:
      type: object
      required:
        - data
        - error
      properties:
        data:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/HealthCheckType"
        error:
          type: object
          nullable: true
          default: null
    HealthCheckType:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          example: director service
        status:
          type: string
          example: SERVICE_RUNNING
        api_version:
          type: string
          example: 1.0.0-dev
        version:
          type: string
          example: 1dfcfdc

# RESPONSES -------------------------------------------------------
  responses:
    EnvelopedDataResponse:
      description: foo
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/EnvelopedData"
